body:
This represents the official release of Apicurio Studio, version 0.2.23.Final.

The following issues have been resolved in this release:

* [#667](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/667) Bump frontend-maven-plugin from 1.6 to 1.7.5
* [#666](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/666) [Security] Bump h2 from 1.4.197 to 1.4.198
* [#665](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/665) Editor: The Add Tag dialog doesn't check if the tag already exists
* [#664](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/664) Editor: When creating a path, the "path already exists" error lags behind the typing
* [#662](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/662) When you try to create security scheme with existing name scheme is not created
* [#660](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/660) Bump gatling-maven-plugin from 3.0.1 to 3.0.2
* [#659](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/659) Bump Java-WebSocket from 1.3.9 to 1.4.0
* [#658](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/658) Editor: Implement "rename" action for all relevant entities
* [#655](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/655) Bump slf4j-api from 1.7.25 to 1.7.26
* [#654](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/654) Bump resteasy-jaxrs from 3.6.2.Final to 3.6.3.Final
* [#653](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/653) Publish: GitHub 'branch' is fetched too early
* [#651](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/651) Bump commons-codec from 1.11 to 1.12
* [#650](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/650) Bump commons-pool2 from 2.6.0 to 2.6.1
* [#648](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/648) Bump javaee-api from 7.0 to 8.0
* [#647](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/647) Bump arquillian-bom from 1.1.13.Final to 1.4.1.Final
* [#646](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/pull/646) Add support for a JMS based shared editing session
* [#641](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/641) Issue: Request Body is not supported for DELETE but RFC 7231 doesn't forbid it
* [#523](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/523) Editor: Prevent use of white spaces in path template when creating Path Items
* [#516](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/516) Editor: Update the L&F of the Rename Data Type dialog
* [#452](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/452) Editor: Rename query parameters
* [#440](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/440) Editor: source edit is not reflected in the Design view
* [#299](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-studio/issues/299) UX: Update Rename Definition dialog with dialog treatment


For more information, please see the Apicurio Studio's official project site:

* [General Information](http://www.apicur.io/)
* [Download/Quickstart](http://www.apicur.io/download)
* [Blog](http://www.apicur.io/blog)
name: Beta 2.23
